# you with Makerules to ease this, here is a sample Makefile.am to use with
# AutoTroll which builds the code given in the chapter 7 of the Qt Tutorial:
# http://doc.trolltech.com/4.2/tutorial-t7.html
#
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
